O‍enttoni menddis moddganchea bodd'ddem vattharantolo.Tacho zolm' 28 ddisembor 1920 hea disa zalo.Tache xikop mumbyont sant terezha ixkolant zale.Lhanuch astona taka tiatrant nhespachi audd asli taka lagun vaddeantlea bhurgeank gheun to lhan lhan kareavolli concert kortalo.Xallent xiktana tachea xikxokan taka iglix concertto pez boi (page boy)chi parot dili ti tanne bhes re toren pall'lli.Oxe toren apli bhineachi kola to fuloupak laglo.[1]

1936 vorsa zuamv agostin fernandis aplea ‘kapri chakor’ hea tiatrant taka lhanxi parot dil'li. Ani oxe toren tanne taka aplea choxea tiatramni vattekar kel'lo.To ek boroupi,bosoupi,rochpi,gaupi ani namnecho vinodi nott.To ixkolant astonach tiatr boroupak survat kel'li tannem vott'tt 15 tiatr boroun macher haddle.Tacho poilo tiatr ‘panddu barber’ (pandu barber)gõyant proyog zalo.Tache kaim her tiatr mhollear ‘artimijh’, ‘gõykar,’ ‘pesamv va tensamv,’‘kunnbi irmamv,’ ‘dusreponni kazar,’tikhli sun,’ ‘vonecho zurament,’‘bekar zamvoi,’ ‘rodd ttu mhapsa,’‘girannacho put,’ adim.[2]

tachea godd avazak lagun to prekxokam modi khub gajil'lo.Tannem mhonnil'lim kantram aiz pasun lokanchea tonddar gollttat.Tachea mhonnpache pod'dotik lagun lok taka spring man mhonnttale.Ek fakiunt hasounno kolakar mhunn tachi namna zal'li.Tachea bhesak pollounuch prekxok hamspak lagtale.Ani taka lagun eka tiatristan taka ‘komiddiyona modlo ek huxar komeddiyon’ mhunn namv dil'lem.‘amche noxib’ filmant to khub porzoll'llo.Oxe toren aplea jivnachi 25 vorsam konknni machechi seva keli ani 21 march 1964 disa to somvsarant ontorolo.

